p.cl:
With these witnesses: the lord William son of John; the lord Walter of Ryedale;
                  Ralph of Ryedale; Adam of Whitton and his sons; Adam of
                  Wauchope; John son of Adam of Chatto; Robert of Bernoldby and
                  Robert his brother; Alexander of Lilliesleaf; Henry de Heriz;
                  Richard the abbot's man; and many others.
